		(property "Description" "The ESP32-S3-DEVKITC-1-N32R8V by Espressif Systems is an advanced evaluation board designed for wireless applications. It features a memory configuration with 32MB Octal SPI Flash and 8MB Octal PSRAM, providing ample storage and memory for complex processing tasks. Powered by the ESP32-S3-WROOM-2-N32R8V module, this board delivers efficient performance with its 32-bit Xtensa dual-core processor running at 240MHz."
